{"type":"message","id":"49ac1a0c","parentId":"df1d148f","timestamp":"2026-04-25T23:59:57.248Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_kgg737nVqYHxe3oYd7gZkNFl|fc_08960d4316f6d9700169ed557648c48195a05c418200e3a8f0","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/openclaw/node_modules/openclaw/docs/concepts/agent-loop.md:154:- LLM idle timeout: `agents.defaults.llm.idleTimeoutSeconds` aborts a model request when no response chunks arrive before the idle window. Set it explicitly for slow local models or reasoning/tool-call providers; set it to 0 to disable. If it is not set, OpenClaw uses `agents.defaults.timeoutSeconds` when configured, otherwise 120s. Cron-triggered runs with no explicit LLM or agent timeout disable the idle watchdog and rely on the cron outer timeout.\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/openclaw/node_modules/openclaw/dist/plugin-sdk/src/config/types.agent-defaults.d.ts:444:    idleTimeoutSeconds?: number;\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/openclaw/node_modules/openclaw/dist/plugin-sdk/src/config/zod-schema.agent-defaults.d.ts:232:        idleTimeoutSeconds: z.ZodOptional<z.ZodNumber>;\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/openclaw/node_modules/openclaw/dist/plugin-sdk/src/config/zod-schema.agents.d.ts:233:            idleTimeoutSeconds: z.ZodOptional<z.ZodNumber>;\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/openclaw/node_modules/openclaw/dist/plugin-sdk/src/config/zod-schema.d.ts:742:                idleTimeoutSeconds: z.ZodOptional<z.ZodNumber>;\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/openclaw/node_modules/openclaw/dist/pi-embedded-runner-CefZK1Pt.js:4739:\tconst raw = params?.cfg?.agents?.defaults?.llm?.idleTimeoutSeconds;\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/openclaw/node_modules/openclaw/dist/pi-embedded-runner-CefZK1Pt.js:8941:\t\t\t\t\t\tconst timeoutText = idleTimedOut ? \"The model did not produce a response before the LLM idle timeout. Please try again, or increase `agents.defaults.llm.idleTimeoutSeconds` in your config (set to 0 to disable).\" : \"Request timed out before a response was generated. Please try again, or increase `agents.defaults.timeoutSeconds` in your config.\";\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/openclaw/node_modules/openclaw/dist/runtime-schema-tlBApuf-.js:4661:\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tproperties: { idleTimeoutSeconds: {\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/openclaw/node_modules/openclaw/dist/zod-schema-BVzBKDrO.js:137:\tllm: z.object({ idleTimeoutSeconds: z.number().int().nonnegative().optional().describe(`Idle timeout for LLM streaming responses in seconds. If no token is received within this time, the request is aborted. Set to 0 to disable. Default: 120 seconds.`) }).strict().optional(),\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/openclaw/node_modules/openclaw/docs/concepts/agent-loop.md:154:- LLM idle timeout: `agents.defaults.llm.idleTimeoutSeconds` aborts a model request when no response chunks arrive before the idle window. Set it explicitly for slow local models or reasoning/tool-call providers; set it to 0 to disable. If it is not set, OpenClaw uses `agents.defaults.timeoutSeconds` when configured, otherwise 120s. Cron-triggered runs with no explicit LLM or agent timeout disable the idle watchdog and rely on the cron outer timeout.\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/openclaw/node_modules/openclaw/CHANGELOG.md:295:- Agents/timeouts: make the LLM idle timeout inherit `agents.defaults.timeoutSeconds` when configured, disable the unconfigured idle watchdog for cron runs, and point idle-timeout errors at `agents.defaults.llm.idleTimeoutSeconds`. Thanks @drvoss."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":4500,"aggregated":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/openclaw/node_modules/openclaw/docs/concepts/agent-loop.md:154:- LLM idle timeout: `agents.defaults.llm.idleTimeoutSeconds` aborts a model request when no response chunks arrive before the idle window. Set it explicitly for slow local models or reasoning/tool-call providers; set it to 0 to disable. If it is not set, OpenClaw uses `agents.defaults.timeoutSeconds` when configured, otherwise 120s. Cron-triggered runs with no explicit LLM or agent timeout disable the idle watchdog and rely on the cron outer timeout.\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/openclaw/node_modules/openclaw/dist/plugin-sdk/src/config/types.agent-defaults.d.ts:444:    idleTimeoutSeconds?: number;\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/openclaw/node_modules/openclaw/dist/plugin-sdk/src/config/zod-schema.agent-defaults.d.ts:232:        idleTimeoutSeconds: z.ZodOptional<z.ZodNumber>;\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/openclaw/node_modules/openclaw/dist/plugin-sdk/src/config/zod-schema.agents.d.ts:233:            idleTimeoutSeconds: z.ZodOptional<z.ZodNumber>;\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/openclaw/node_modules/openclaw/dist/plugin-sdk/src/config/zod-schema.d.ts:742:                idleTimeoutSeconds: z.ZodOptional<z.ZodNumber>;\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/openclaw/node_modules/openclaw/dist/pi-embedded-runner-CefZK1Pt.js:4739:\tconst raw = params?.cfg?.agents?.defaults?.llm?.idleTimeoutSeconds;\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/openclaw/node_modules/openclaw/dist/pi-embedded-runner-CefZK1Pt.js:8941:\t\t\t\t\t\tconst timeoutText = idleTimedOut ? \"The model did not produce a response before the LLM idle timeout. Please try again, or increase `agents.defaults.llm.idleTimeoutSeconds` in your config (set to 0 to disable).\" : \"Request timed out before a response was generated. Please try again, or increase `agents.defaults.timeoutSeconds` in your config.\";\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/openclaw/node_modules/openclaw/dist/runtime-schema-tlBApuf-.js:4661:\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tproperties: { idleTimeoutSeconds: {\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/openclaw/node_modules/openclaw/dist/zod-schema-BVzBKDrO.js:137:\tllm: z.object({ idleTimeoutSeconds: z.number().int().nonnegative().optional().describe(`Idle timeout for LLM streaming responses in seconds. If no token is received within this time, the request is aborted. Set to 0 to disable. Default: 120 seconds.`) }).strict().optional(),\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/openclaw/node_modules/openclaw/docs/concepts/agent-loop.md:154:- LLM idle timeout: `agents.defaults.llm.idleTimeoutSeconds` aborts a model request when no response chunks arrive before the idle window. Set it explicitly for slow local models or reasoning/tool-call providers; set it to 0 to disable. If it is not set, OpenClaw uses `agents.defaults.timeoutSeconds` when configured, otherwise 120s. Cron-triggered runs with no explicit LLM or agent timeout disable the idle watchdog and rely on the cron outer timeout.\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/openclaw/node_modules/openclaw/CHANGELOG.md:295:- Agents/timeouts: make the LLM idle timeout inherit `agents.defaults.timeoutSeconds` when configured, disable the unconfigured idle watchdog for cron runs, and point idle-timeout errors at `agents.defaults.llm.idleTimeoutSeconds`. Thanks @drvoss.","cwd":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777161597176}}
{"type":"message","id":"717df435","parentId":"49ac1a0c","timestamp":"2026-04-26T00:00:00.625Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_eqJGVV66P3cpmYuhV49zatPp|fc_08960d4316f6d9700169ed557f933c8195beea0075a20c01fc","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/openclaw/node_modules/openclaw/docs/concepts/agent-loop.md","offset":145,"limit":30},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/openclaw/node_modules/openclaw/docs/concepts/agent-loop.md\",\"offset\":145,\"limit\":30}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":11373,"output":51,"cacheRead":35328,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46752,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777161597251,"responseId":"resp_08960d4316f6d9700169ed557e685881958850fa0e490d9ed8"}}
{"type":"message","id":"82a74101","parentId":"717df435","timestamp":"2026-04-26T00:00:00.808Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_eqJGVV66P3cpmYuhV49zatPp|fc_08960d4316f6d9700169ed557f933c8195beea0075a20c01fc","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Chat channel handling\n\n- Assistant deltas are buffered into chat `delta` messages.\n- A chat `final` is emitted on **lifecycle end/error**.\n\n## Timeouts\n\n- `agent.wait` default: 30s (just the wait). `timeoutMs` param overrides.\n- Agent runtime: `agents.defaults.timeoutSeconds` default 172800s (48 hours); enforced in `runEmbeddedPiAgent` abort timer.\n- LLM idle timeout: `agents.defaults.llm.idleTimeoutSeconds` aborts a model request when no response chunks arrive before the idle window. Set it explicitly for slow local models or reasoning/tool-call providers; set it to 0 to disable. If it is not set, OpenClaw uses `agents.defaults.timeoutSeconds` when configured, otherwise 120s. Cron-triggered runs with no explicit LLM or agent timeout disable the idle watchdog and rely on the cron outer timeout.\n\n## Where things can end early\n\n- Agent timeout (abort)\n- AbortSignal (cancel)\n- Gateway disconnect or RPC timeout\n- `agent.wait` timeout (wait-only, does not stop agent)\n\n## Related\n\n- [Tools](/tools) — available agent tools\n- [Hooks](/automation/hooks) — event-driven scripts triggered by agent lifecycle events\n- [Compaction](/concepts/compaction) — how long conversations are summarized\n- [Exec Approvals](/tools/exec-approvals) — approval gates for shell commands\n- [Thinking](/tools/thinking) — thinking/reasoning level configuration\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777161600743}}
{"type":"message","id":"97739b85","parentId":"82a74101","timestamp":"2026-04-26T00:00:11.351Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"这个报错的意思很明确：\n\n**模型太久没有产出流式响应，触发了 OpenClaw 的 LLM 空闲超时。**\n\n你这边最直接的处理是改 `openclaw.json` 里的这一段：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"defaults\": {\n      \"llm\": {\n        \"idleTimeoutSeconds\": 300\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n如果你想**彻底关闭这个空闲超时**，就改成：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"defaults\": {\n      \"llm\": {\n        \"idleTimeoutSeconds\": 0\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 你的当前配置文件\n路径是：\n\n`/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/openclaw.json`\n\n### 建议怎么选\n- **先试 300 秒**：更稳，适合慢模型、修图、生图、长工具调用\n- **设 0**：完全不拦，但如果模型真卡死，会等很久\n\n### 你现在为什么会遇到\n你当前配置里我已经看过，**还没有 `agents.defaults.llm.idleTimeoutSeconds`**，所以它走默认行为。文档写的是：\n\n- 若未设置，默认会用 `agents.defaults.timeoutSeconds`\n- 若也没配，就默认 **120 秒**\n\n所以你现在基本就是 **120 秒没流出内容就被中断**。\n\n### 文档依据\nSource: `/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/openclaw/node_modules/openclaw/docs/concepts/agent-loop.md#154`\n\n### 改完后\n通常需要让 OpenClaw 重新加载配置，最稳妥是重启一下 gateway 或主进程。\n\n如果你愿意，我可以直接帮你把配置改成 **300 秒**。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_08960d4316f6d9700169ed5583ab48819594a598f4197b97af\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":5099,"output":412,"cacheRead":41984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47495,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777161600812,"responseId":"resp_08960d4316f6d9700169ed5581f2d48195bb773aed08456a23"}}
