{"type":"message","id":"300fa4e8","parentId":"78818620","timestamp":"2026-04-26T00:02:58.654Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 我这边直接重启时发现不是“重启失败”，而是 **gateway 服务当前并没有作为 systemd 服务启用**。\n\n返回的是：\n- `Gateway service disabled.`\n- 建议启动方式之一：\n  - `openclaw gateway`\n  - `systemctl --user start openclaw-gateway.service`\n  - 或先 `openclaw gateway install`\n\n**结论**\n你这台环境现在更像是前台 / 非 systemd 方式在跑，所以 `restart` 没法按服务方式重启。\n\n**最小下一步**\n你现在直接运行这个最合适：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway\n```\n\n如果你希望，我下一步可以继续帮你做两件事里的一个：\n1. **检查当前 gateway 到底是怎么跑起来的**，然后给你最稳的重启方式  \n2. **指导你把它装成 systemd 用户服务**，以后就能直接 `openclaw gateway restart`","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_08960d4316f6d9700169ed562e75388195b23400d2d6c1d53e\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":48524,"output":218,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48742,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777161772134,"responseId":"resp_08960d4316f6d9700169ed562d43608195b7ef46d3fb0b7b6b"}}
