{"type":"message","id":"44256d70","parentId":"4b799389","timestamp":"2026-04-26T10:26:01.333Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 可以。  \n我直接给你做成**带文案的电商页版本**。\n\n你只要再给我这 3 样里的任意一种，我就能直接开做：\n\n1. **产品卖点文案**  \n   例如：防水、防滑、耐磨、轻便、透气\n\n2. **产品名称 + slogan**  \n   例如：  \n   - 名称：轻奢防滑凉拖  \n   - slogan：一步到位的舒适感\n\n3. **让我自由发挥**  \n   我会按图片内容自动配：\n   - 主标题\n   - 2 到 4 个卖点\n   - 简短购买引导文案\n\n如果你想省事，直接回我一句：\n\n**自由发挥，直接做**\n\n我就马上出图。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_08960d4316f6d9700169ede83564e4819580972fa79136348b\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":98147,"output":191,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98338,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777199151910,"responseId":"resp_08960d4316f6d9700169ede831c1088195bf983ed97494a40d"}}
